snippet.title: DIY MET GALA INSPIRED HEADPIECES - Blake Lively, Sza, & Amber Heard || Lucykiins
snippet.description:
I got so inspired by all the pretty headpieces at last week's Met Gala so I decided to recreate a few! These were honestly sooo easy to do and all the supplies can be found at your local dollar store or Walmart! Hope you guys enjoy ♥

Don't forget to SUBSCRIBE for more DIYs in the future !
XOXO, Lucero Tapia ♥

FOLLOW ME ♥
https://www.instagram.com/lucykiins/
https://mobile.twitter.com/lucykiins

________________________________________________________________

SUPPLIES:
Headbands - Dollar Store
Hoop Earring - Dollar Store
Skewers - Dollar Store
Zip Ties - Walmart
Floral Wire - Dollar Tree
Sparkle Gems - Walmart
Rhinestones - Dollar King
Gold Spray Paint - Home Depot
Glue Gun
Wire Cutter
